<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Deal Available</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF9933 0%, #138808 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        
        .deal-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #f8f9fa 100%);
            border: 2px solid #FF9933;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .deal-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF9933, #138808);
        }
        
        .new-badge {
            background: #FF9933;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .deal-title {
            color: #138808;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .business-name {
            color: #FF9933;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .deal-description {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .deal-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background: rgba(255, 153, 51, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #FF9933;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .discount-highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF9933, #138808);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .discount-text {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .discount-subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF9933 0%, #138808 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 153, 51, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 153, 51, 0.4);
        }
        
        .validity-notice {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .validity-notice h4 {
            color: #1976d2;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .validity-notice p {
            color: #666;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .deal-details {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .discount-text {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üéâ New Deal Alert!</h1>
            <p>Exclusive offer just for you</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #333;">
                Hi {{firstName}},
            </p>
            
            <p style="margin-bottom: 25px; color: #666;">
                We're excited to share a brand new deal that just went live on our platform!
            </p>
            
            <div class="deal-card">
                <div class="new-badge">New Deal</div>
                <h2 class="deal-title">{{dealTitle}}</h2>
                <p class="business-name">üìç {{businessName}}</p>
                <p class="deal-description">{{dealDescription}}</p>
                
                {{#if discount}}
                <div class="discount-highlight">
                    <div class="discount-text">{{discount}} OFF</div>
                    <div class="discount-subtitle">Limited Time Offer</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                <div class="deal-details">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Business</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{businessName}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{#if validUntil}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Valid Until</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{validUntil}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Category</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">Deal</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="validity-notice">
                <h4>‚è∞ Don't Miss Out!</h4>
                <p>This exclusive deal is available for a limited time. Redeem it now before it expires or reaches its maximum redemption limit.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #f0f8f0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0;">
                <h4 style="color: #138808; margin-bottom: 15px;">üì± How to Redeem:</h4>
                <ol style="color: #666; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Click the button above to view the full deal</li>
                    <li>Click "Redeem Deal" on the deal page</li>
                    <li>Show your QR code to the merchant</li>
                    <li>Enjoy your savings!</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Indians in Ghana</strong> - Connecting Community, Creating Value</p>
            <p>You received this email because you're subscribed to deal notifications.</p>
            <p>This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
            <p>Email: cards@indiansinghana.com | Website: www.indiansinghana.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
